mnemonic seedqr encode
mnemonic seedqr decode
mnemonic xpub-search path-of-xpub
mnemonic xpub-search account-of-descriptor
mnemonic xpub-search address-of-xpub
mnemonic xpub-search passphrase-of-xpub

